Package com.telenav.mesakit.graph.library.osm.change

Class MutableWay

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.mesakit.graph.library.osm.change.BaseMutableWay
com.telenav.mesakit.graph.library.osm.change.MutableWay
public class MutableWay extends BaseMutableWay
A class that holds an OSM way and models any changes that need to be made to nodes that are caused by adding new connections to the way (sometimes a connection can be made to an existing node and sometimes a new node needs to be added because there is no node reasonably close). In addition, holds any road name that has been added if the way is unnamed.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)

      Creates a node to allow a connection at the given location to this OSM way. If there is already a node close enough to the snap location on the way, it will be used. If there is no node close enough, a new node will be added.
